snippet.title: Synapse - Deep Dive Trailer | PS VR2 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/synapse/

Dive deeper into the world of Synapse with this brand-new trailer, revealing how players will be upgrading and evolving their arsenal and telekinetic abilities as they fight deep into the mind of an enemy of the state.  

Synapse launches exclusively for PlayStation VR2 on July 4th.
